For more information about eligibility and registration, please contact your school’s main office. 216-586-3892

Breakthrough Public Schools
December 22, 2018 at 4:29 PM ·

Hey all! Two updates before we all sign off for the holidays!

1) Early Enrollment for 2019/20 school year is Jan 2 - March 7th. If you want to sign up over the break, you can do it here: https://breakthroughschools.schoolmint.net/signup

2) Some families were asking if we have any immediate openings in K-8. We do! We'd love to have you join our community. Openings vary by campus and grade level. Sign up here and we'll contact you about immediate openings: https://breakthroughschools.org/enrollment-updates/

Have great holidays everyone :) We'll be back soon with plenty of updates from our schools!
text:
Breakthrough Public Schools
December 22, 2018 at 4:29 PM ·

Hey all! Two updates before we all sign off for the holidays!

1) Early Enrollment for 2019/20 school year is Jan 2 - March 7th. If you want to sign up over the break, you can do it here: https://breakthroughschools.schoolmint.net/signup

2) Some families were asking if we have any immediate openings in K-8. We do! We'd love to have you join our community. Openings vary by campus and grade level. Sign up here and we'll contact you about immediate openings: https://breakthroughschools.org/enrollment-updates/

Have great holidays everyone :) We'll be back soon with plenty of updates from our schools!

post_text:
This Thanksgiving we are thankful for our scholars who show up ready to learn and try new things each day. We are thankful for our families who trust us wholeheartedly with their most precious gifts. We are thankful for our staff who give 100% of themselves each day to do what’s best for kids. We are thankful for the support of our network and volunteers. Finally, we are thankful for learning because “The beautiful thing about learning is that no one can take it away from you.” - B. B. King

What are you thankful for this Thanksgiving?

#thanksgiving #gratitude #learning #thisiscle #giveback #clevelandfoodbank #villageprepwillard #eprepwillard #btcle #teamworkmakesthedreamwork #collegebound #scholars @ E Prep & Village Prep Willard Campus

post_text:
Hi all! Want to secure your child's spot in our school but haven't completed your application yet? Come to our school on Saturday 7/22 at 11am to our Enrollment Session. You can visit the school, complete your paperwork, and secure your elementary & middle school spot!

Remember: Our school is 100% free, public, and open to all students. We have had a lot of demand at both the elementary and middle school levels, and currently have openings in Grades K-2 and 5-6. We're a high expectations school and focus on college prep for all students. We also have some amazing partnerships with community organizations like Rainey Institute, Urban Squash Cleveland, and STEM Programming through Cleveland Clinic!

Sign up using the link below to let us know if you'll be coming by on Saturday to complete your child's enrollment!
